drandr - dynamic sound
====================
drandr is sound manage util for dwm.


Requirements
------------
In order to build drandr you need the Xlib header files.


Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (drandr is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default).

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install drandr
(if necessary as root):

    make clean install


Running drandr
-------------
See the man page for details.
